latestIgtvVideos.caption:

Every girl has a different training background. @_poojakhandei_ is a classical dancer @rosh_minimax @_pooja_gurnani_ are die hard Hiphop lovers and @taptithakur is an amazing model and a mover. Being this way and still we pulled it off in such a way, I am proud of you my girls.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Freedom to dream ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I am no bird that could be ensnared by a net: I am a free soul with an independent will.  This is what I was taught when I was chirping in my nest.
As I learned to fly, a lot of things changed! Except one, my wings! The wings that soared me high with every  Pirouette.
There was a dream.
A dream to dance on the edge, 
A dream to be a part of something huge, 
The dream was to teach, teach the other birdlings, to hop off their nest, spread their wings and take a leap.
The Dream was to feel, feel the echo of music in my bones, 
A dream to express, express through my moves, 
The dream was to be know for my dance;
There was a dream.
A dream to have freedom to achieve.
Now you may ask whose dream was it?
With a fluttering pride I tell you, it’s My mother’s!
.
@_menonism_ can’t thank you enough for helping me with the poem.
.
Voice - yours truly 🙋🏻‍♀️
Choreography- yours truly 🙋🏻‍♀️
Shot by - @shresth_6116 ♥️
.
I hope you can feel what I felt while I was doing this.♥️

latestIgtvVideos.title: ❗️IMPROVISATION ALERT❗️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Lately I’ve been doing a lot of choreography classes and lost the actual touch of my own movement. I am a very aggressive dancer and my movement quality mostly is all about lines and hits but recently I’ve been doing isolation and the body feels different while I do that. Tapping into both movements is difficult but that’s my thing because as much as I love staccato movements, I’m falling for being fluid in the same manner.
.
Uploading a very different content this time. Not a choreography just the improv.
.
Thanks @kirtishankar_24 for getting me back into improvisation. This feels so good.
.
Song - Human by @aquilo 
.
*I DO NOT OWN THE RIGHTS TO THE MUSIC. JUST FOR ENTERTAINMENT PURPOSES ONLY.*
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: I AM HUMAN!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This choreography isn’t difficult by steps but it’s difficult to get the character. This is the second time I’m trying this song and this time it feels fulfilling. .
I could feel like I’m not a human at all but trying to a prove myself to be a human to get society’s acceptance. .
Everyone is different from each other and to be accepted in the society, we tend to pretend to be someone else. .
Imagine how the world will look like if we can be ourselves around every one. How pure it will be.
.
Thanks @mukta_nagpal for teaching this amazing choreography. I can’t even explain how much I’m missing your classes. Thanks for always showing trust in me. .
Video details:-
Choreography- @mukta_nagpal ♥️.
.
Song- Human by @sevdaliza_ .
.
Dancer- @sakshiiiiiiiiiigupta .
.
